{"tid":2063684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維尼係咪一早知北京爆到仆街所以一早走去寧夏睇窿避難","createTime":"2020-06-14T08:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T08:47:04.000Z","uid":58841,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb1aa08557e666f9974f7dc6141a197228ea1f7","tid":2063684,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:13:47.000Z","msg":"牆內人係咁講的<br />\n<br />\n「好吧现在这算是第二轮爆发还是第三轮？<br />\n<br />\n截至目前北京公布的三例确诊病例<span style=\"color: red;\">全部和新发地有交集，而且其中两个人是肉类食品检测员，走遍了北京所有的农贸批发市场和一部分菜市场</span>」<br />\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/id-20310__sort-DESC__sort_key-agree_count__page-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2Fid-20310__sort-DESC__sort_key-agree_count__page-2&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=b0f2c954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/id-20310__sort-DESC__sort_key-agree_count__page-2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母真係咁既話成個北京唔洗要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落難皇帝習維尼<br />\n唔怪得前幾日無鳩拿拿有新聞講維尼去左睇窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803c998d27424185ca1b8dd0714f42a343801174","tid":2063684,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"根本一直都仲係第一輪爆發無停過"},{"pid":"e35ed977849974615620bdbc088f54c6a8f53ad1","tid":2063684,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"寧下有鑛場"},{"pid":"dd4c9c7f710c0095587a7330b24bb1bc84444310","tid":2063684,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"803c998d27424185ca1b8dd0714f42a343801174","tid":2063684,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"根本一直都仲係第一輪爆發無停過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:16:21.000Z","msg":"有兩條友行均哂成個北京街市<br />\n即刻啲野食可以唔洗要咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2abe0eda3ea4254ba0276ba36faa700e9fc54e","tid":2063684,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"到底雜種自從開完個共狗會之後去左邊?"},{"pid":"cd073f8459a04ec125b49451462668bddfd7cb27","tid":2063684,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"首都戶籍咪又係韮菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d6effb8024cef61734085ea7e9c347375782d8","tid":2063684,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"好似金正恩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab1981b501bd1c0b4c9e0dfc4e91ca54788b386","tid":2063684,"uid":301952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6f2abe0eda3ea4254ba0276ba36faa700e9fc54e","tid":2063684,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"到底雜種自從開完個共狗會之後去左邊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"升中學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5907d68cb6c286e04830397b275f7bf3f46293b0","tid":2063684,"uid":20170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"803c998d27424185ca1b8dd0714f42a343801174","tid":2063684,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"根本一直都仲係第一輪爆發無停過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:18:19.000Z","msg":"心水Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09e86760eccadcebc64df611fa4c614434d735c","tid":2063684,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"別讓習近平跑了"},{"pid":"df35b9cc3fc7101a7e8247bc042a9b66d7e3f334","tid":2063684,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:19:14.000Z","msg":"https://www. <a href=\"http://cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006130134.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202006130134.aspx&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=82e652bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006130134.aspx</a> <br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北13日電）北京近日2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情又起，且出現跨省傳播。據遼寧省衛健委官網，當地12日出現新增無症狀感染者2例，都是北京市12日報告的確診病例的密切接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n北京近日新一波疫情受到關注，原本已連續56天無新增的武漢肺炎本土病例，卻在11日起至今共出現7例本土確診病例，並在新發地農產品批發市場發現共有45名從業人員的咽喉拭子病毒檢測呈陽性反應。<span style=\"color: red;\">今天更證實相關確診病例已跨省傳播至遼寧</span>。<br />\n<br />\n此外，北京豐台區12日確診的病例中，劉姓患者自述近2週曾到山東省青島市出差5天，根據青島衛健委，已排除這名患者是在青島感染的可能。<span style=\"color: red;\">自11日起，北京7例武漢肺炎確診患者，全都與豐台區的新發地市場有關。</span><br />\n<br />\n面對疫情擴大，北京市平谷區衛健委下午發布疫情防控情況通報稱，12日區疾控中心已對重點場所和人群進行檢測，密切接觸者及外環境新冠病毒核酸檢測結果均為陰性。截止13日12時，全區未出現確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n各國大使館聚集的朝陽區，今天上午召開疫情防控工作領導小組會議強調，要進一步研究調度全區疫情防控工作，要從嚴從快對近14天內到過新發地農產品批發市場的人員，全面開展流調、溯源、檢測、排查。（編輯：張淑伶/林克倫）1090613"},{"pid":"c19f8edef235bdc074ef990e6c0c20c1a224e8e8","tid":2063684,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"佢就黎係支那都無地方比佢避架啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c3bd40a3beb94655b23609d6191958531e51cc","tid":2063684,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c19f8edef235bdc074ef990e6c0c20c1a224e8e8","tid":2063684,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"佢就黎係支那都無地方比佢避架啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:23:13.000Z","msg":"搵左下遼寧係邊<br />\n原來就係金仔隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44nr0Ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44nr0Ca.png&h=a919b92b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支那仲有邊啲地方可以俾佢避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf6063ab11a1ccf0a4732aa979e17a5065fecbd","tid":2063684,"uid":182822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:39:06.000Z","msg":"咸豐十年八月（1860年），英法聯軍在第二次鴉片戰爭中攻破大沽口，佔領天津。隨後在八里橋擊潰了清軍的精銳，京師危在旦夕。9月22日，咸豐帝率包含慈禧在內的一干宮眷逃往熱河避暑山莊避難，留恭親王奕訢在京師與聯軍議和。英法聯軍在北京大肆搶劫後，10月18日將包括圓明園在內的皇家「三山五園」焚燒，大火燒了三天三夜。<br />\n啊雜種覺得呢排天時熱走去避暑姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2c384d206fad30de6ed2e738822f38fdc4de19","tid":2063684,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:47:04.000Z","msg":"仲有支那作野都作好啲啦<br />\n作魚傳人仲大獲過人傳人<br />\n人死左可以釘落棺材<br />\n但係話魚有病毒即係講全世界既水域都有傳染風險<br />\n你又搵唔到傳染源係邊<br />\n咁即係支那糧食危機一定黎梗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}